Package com.virginmoneygiving.connect.sdk.v1.beans.fundraiser.response

Bean classes which represent the business objects returned from the VMG /fundraisers/v1/ API.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AccessTokenDetails Contains the details of a valid access token after the authorisation code has been successfully exchanged via POST API call, or if the call fails, the error code and details.
ActivityType Contains the details for a single activity from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/activities".
ActivityTypes Contains the list of activities from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/activities".
Address Contains the details for a single address from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/postcode".
Addresses Contains the list of addresses from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/postcode".
CharityDetails Contains the details for a single charity on a page from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/.../page".
Countries Contains the list of countries from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/countries".
Country Contains the details of a single country from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/countries".
Fundraiser Contains the details of a fundraiser after a successsful creation via POST API call to "/fundraisers/v1/newaccount"
FundraiserDetail Contains the details for a single fundraiser from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/.../page".
FundraiserPageSummary Contains the details of a single fundraiser page after a GET API call to "/fundraisers/v1/".
FundraiserSearchResult Contains the details of a single fundraiser after a GET API call to "/fundraisers/v1/search".
FundraiserSearchResults Contains the list of fundraisers after a GET API call to "/fundraisers/v1/search".
FundraiserSummary Contains the details of a single fundraiser after a GET API call to "/fundraisers/v1/".
Page Contains the details of a fundraiser page after a successsful creation via POST API call to "/fundraisers/v1/account/secure/..../newpage"
PageDetails Contains the details for a single page from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/.../page".
TeamMember Contains the details for a single fundraiser team member from the result of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/.../page".
UrlCheck Contains the results from of a GET API call to "fundraisers/v1/urls".
